    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯考虑将汽油出口许可延长至 6 月之后</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/russia-mulls-extending-gasoline-export-permission-beyond-june</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，由于国内供应仍然充足，俄罗斯正考虑允许其炼油厂在 6 月份以后继续出口汽油。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/russia-mulls-extending-gasoline-export-permission-beyond-june</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 06:26:10 GMT</pubDate>
