    <item>
      <title>英国通胀率三年来首次放缓至 2% 目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/uk-inflation-back-at-2-goal-first-time-in-almost-three-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国通胀率近三年来首次回落至英国央行2%的目标，这一里程碑可能来得太晚，无法在即将到来的大选之前改善首相里希·苏纳克的政治命运。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/uk-inflation-back-at-2-goal-first-time-in-almost-three-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 06:02:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Polus Capital Management 的 Dafforn：我们正处于信贷利差非常紧张的时期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-19/dafforn-we-re-in-a-period-of-very-tight-credit-spreads-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着交易流程变得越来越复杂，投资者对私人资本市场抱有很大的乐观态度。Polus Capital Management Opportunistic Credit 首席信息官 Robert Dafforn 就该领域值得担忧的问题发表了自己的看法。Dafforn 在《彭博今日市场》节目中与 Kriti Gupta、Anna Edwards 和 Guy Johnson 进行了交谈。此次采访于 6 月 18 日星期二进行。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-19/dafforn-we-re-in-a-period-of-very-tight-credit-spreads-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 05:48:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
